  }
  
  .auth-links a {
    color: #667eea;
    text-decoration: none;
    margin: 0 15px;
  }
  
  .auth-links a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .refund-container {
      margin: 10px;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }
    
    .refund-header h1 {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }
    
    .refund-content h2 {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      margin-top: 25px;
    }
    
    .refund-content h3 {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }
    
    .refund-content p {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    
    .refund-table {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      display: block;
      overflow-x: auto;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
    
    .refund-table th,
    .refund-table td {
      padding: 6px;
      min-width: 100px;
    }
    
    .policy-highlight,
    .warning-box,
    .process-steps,
    .contact-info {
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    
    .auth-links {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
    
    .auth-links a {
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 5px 8px;
    }
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .refund-container {
      margin: 5px;
      padding: 15px;
    }
    
    .refund-header h1 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .refund-content h2 {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    
    .refund-content h3 {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
    
    .refund-content p {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
    
    .refund-table {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
    }
    
    .refund-table th,
    .refund-table td {
      padding: 4px;
      min-width: 80px;
    }
    
    .policy-highlight h3,
    .warning-box h3,
    .process-steps h3,
    .contact-info h3 {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
    
    .auth-links a {
      display: block;
      margin: 8px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
  }
</style>

<div class="refund-container">
  <div class="refund-header">
    <h1>Refund Policy</h1>
    <p class="last-updated">Last Updated: <%= new Date().toLocaleDateString() %></p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="refund-content">
    <div class="policy-highlight">
      <h3>üí∞ Our Fair Refund Promise</h3>
      <p>At Fairytale Genie, we want you to be completely satisfied with our service. We offer a straightforward refund policy designed to be fair to both our customers and our business.</p>
    </div>

    <h2>1. Free Trial Period</h2>
    <p>All new subscribers receive a <strong>3-day free trial</strong> when they first sign up for Fairytale Genie Premium. During this trial period:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>You have full access to all premium features</li>
      <li>You can cancel at any time without charge</li>
      <li>No refund is necessary as you haven't been charged yet</li>
      <li>Your subscription will automatically begin after the trial ends</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="policy-highlight">
      <h3>üí∞ 10-Day No Questions Asked Refund Guarantee</h3>
      <p>We stand behind our service with a simple promise: <strong>Request a full refund within 10 days of your first billing date for any reason, no questions asked.</strong></p>
    </div>

    <h2>2. Refund Eligibility</h2>
    <table class="refund-table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Situation</th>
          <th>Refund Available</th>
          <th>Conditions</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Within First 10 Days</strong><br>Any reason at all</td>
          <td>‚úÖ Full Refund</td>
          <td><strong>No questions asked - guaranteed refund</strong></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Technical Issues</strong><br>Service unavailable or malfunctioning</td>
          <td>‚úÖ Full Refund</td>
          <td>Must report within 30 days of billing</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Billing Errors</strong><br>Incorrect charges or duplicate billing</td>
          <td>‚úÖ Full Refund</td>
          <td>Must report within 30 days</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Account Compromise</strong><br>Unauthorized use of account</td>
          <td>‚úÖ Full Refund</td>
          <td>Must report immediately and cooperate with investigation</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>After 10-Day Period</strong><br>General dissatisfaction</td>
          <td>‚ö†Ô∏è Case-by-Case</td>
          <td>We'll work with you to find a fair solution</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h2>3. Refund Timeframes</h2>
    <h3>When You Can Request a Refund:</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>No Questions Asked:</strong> Within 10 days of your first billing date</li>
      <li><strong>Technical Issues:</strong> Within 30 days of the billing date</li>
      <li><strong>Billing Errors:</strong> Within 30 days of the charge</li>
      <li><strong>Unauthorized Charges:</strong> Within 60 days of discovery</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="warning-box">
      <h3>‚ö†Ô∏è Important Limitations</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Refunds are only available for the most recent billing cycle</li>
        <li>Excessive refund requests may result in account termination</li>
        <li>Refunds for gift subscriptions follow the same policy</li>
        <li>Processing fees (where applicable) are non-refundable</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <h2>4. How to Request a Refund</h2>
    <div class="process-steps">
      <h3>üìã Refund Request Process</h3>
      <ol>
        <li><strong>Contact Support:</strong> Email us at info@fairytalegenie.com with your account details</li>
        <li><strong>Provide Information:</strong> Include your reason for the refund request and relevant details</li>
        <li><strong>Wait for Review:</strong> We'll review your request within 2-3 business days</li>
        <li><strong>Receive Decision:</strong> You'll get an email with our decision and next steps</li>
        <li><strong>Processing:</strong> Approved refunds are processed within 5-7 business days</li>
      </ol>
    </div>

    <h3>Required Information for Refund Requests:</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Account email address</li>
      <li>Approximate date of the charge</li>
      <li>Reason for refund request</li>
      <li>Any relevant screenshots or error messages</li>
      <li>Last 4 digits of the payment method used</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>5. Refund Processing</h2>
    <h3>Processing Times:</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Credit Cards:</strong> 5-7 business days</li>
      <li><strong>PayPal:</strong> 3-5 business days</li>
      <li><strong>Bank Transfers:</strong> 7-10 business days</li>
    </ul>

    <p><strong>Note:</strong> Refund processing times depend on your payment provider and may take longer during holidays or weekends.</p>

    <h2>6. Cancellation vs. Refund</h2>
    <h3>Cancellation:</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Stops future billing immediately</li>
      <li>You keep access until the end of your current billing period</li>
      <li>No refund for the current period (unless eligible above)</li>
      <li>Can be done anytime through your account settings</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Refund:</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Returns money for current or recent billing period</li>
      <li>May result in immediate loss of access to premium features</li>
      <li>Requires approval based on our refund policy</li>
      <li>Must be requested through customer support</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>7. Special Circumstances</h2>
    <h3>Family Accounts:</h3>
    <p>For accounts primarily used by children under 18, parents/guardians can request refunds on behalf of their family members under the same conditions as regular accounts.</p>

    <h3>Educational Discounts:</h3>
    <p>Accounts with educational discounts follow the same refund policy, but the refund amount will be based on the discounted price paid.</p>

    <h2>8. Dispute Resolution</h2>
    <p>If you're not satisfied with our refund decision:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>You can appeal by providing additional information</li>
      <li>We'll conduct a secondary review within 5 business days</li>
      <li>For unresolved disputes, you may contact your payment provider</li>
      <li>Legal disputes are subject to binding arbitration as outlined in our Terms of Service</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="contact-info">
      <h3>üìß Contact Information</h3>
      <p>For refund requests or questions about this policy:</p>
      <p><strong>Email:</strong> info@fairytalegenie.com</p>
      <p><strong>Response Time:</strong> We aim to respond to all refund requests within 24-48 hours</p>
    </div>

    <h2>9. Policy Changes</h2>
    <p>We reserve the right to modify this refund policy at any time. Changes will:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Be posted on this page with an updated "Last Updated" date</li>
      <li>Be communicated to active subscribers via email</li>
      <li>Take effect 30 days after notification</li>
      <li>Not affect refund requests submitted before the change</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  
  <div class="auth-links">
    <a href="/pricing">Pricing</a>
    <a href="/terms">Terms of Service</a>
    <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>
    <a href="/auth/login">Join Waitlist</a>
  </div>
</div>